<template>
  <v-container fluid class="down-top-padding">
    <BaseBreadcrumb :title="page.title" :icon="page.icon" :breadcrumbs="breadcrumbs"></BaseBreadcrumb>
    <v-row>
      <v-col cols="12" sm="12" lg="6">
        <BaseCard heading="Toolbar - Prominent toolbars">
          <ToolbarProminent></ToolbarProminent>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>

      <v-col cols="12" sm="12" lg="6">
        <BaseCard heading="Toolbar - Dense toolbars">
          <ToolbarDence></ToolbarDence>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>

      <v-col cols="12" sm="12" lg="6">
        <BaseCard heading="Toolbar - Contextual action bars">
          <ToolbarContextualActionbar></ToolbarContextualActionbar>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>

      <v-col cols="12" sm="12" lg="6">
        <BaseCard heading="Toolbar - Collapse">
          <ToolbarCollapse></ToolbarCollapse>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>

      <v-col cols="12" sm="12" lg="6">
        <BaseCard heading="Toolbar - Floating with search">
          <ToolbarFloatingSearch></ToolbarFloatingSearch>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>

      <v-col cols="12" sm="12" lg="6">
        <BaseCard heading="Toolbar - Flexible toolbar and card toolbar">
          <ToolbarFlexibleCard></ToolbarFlexibleCard>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>

      <v-col cols="12" sm="12" lg="6">
        <BaseCard heading="Toolbar - Extended">
          <ToolbarExtended></ToolbarExtended>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>

      <v-col cols="12" sm="12" lg="6">
        <BaseCard heading="Toolbar - Extension height">
          <ToolbarExtendedHeight></ToolbarExtendedHeight>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>

      <v-col cols="12" sm="12">
        <BaseCard heading="Toolbar - Light and Dark">
          <ToolbarLightDark></ToolbarLightDark>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Toolbar - Variations">
          <ToolbarVariations></ToolbarVariations>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Toolbar - Prominent w/ Background">
          <ToolbarProminentBackground></ToolbarProminentBackground>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "Toolbar",

  data: () => ({
    page: {
      title: "Toolbar"
    },
    breadcrumbs: [
      {
        text: "UI Components",
        disabled: false,
        to: "#"
      },
      {
        text: "Toolbar",
        disabled: true
      }
    ]
  }),
  components: {
    ToolbarProminent: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/toolbar/ToolbarProminent"),
    ToolbarDence: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/toolbar/ToolbarDence"),
    ToolbarContextualActionbar: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/toolbar/ToolbarContextualActionbar"
      ),
    ToolbarCollapse: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/toolbar/ToolbarCollapse"),
    ToolbarFloatingSearch: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/toolbar/ToolbarFloatingSearch"),
    ToolbarFlexibleCard: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/toolbar/ToolbarFlexibleCard"),
    ToolbarExtended: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/toolbar/ToolbarExtended"),
    ToolbarExtendedHeight: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/toolbar/ToolbarExtendedHeight"),
    ToolbarLightDark: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/toolbar/ToolbarLightDark"),
    ToolbarVariations: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/toolbar/ToolbarVariations"),
    ToolbarProminentBackground: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/toolbar/ToolbarProminentBackground"
      )
  }
};
</script>
